<button class="accordion">What do you mean by dementia?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Dementia describes a group of symptoms affecting memory, thinking and social abilities severely enough to interfere with your daily life. Though dementia generally involves memory loss, memory loss has different causes. Having memory loss alone does not mean you have dementia.</p>
