</div>
<button class="accordion">What is the best definition of dementia?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>It is usually progressive condition (such as Alzheimer's disease) marked by the development of multiple cognitive deficits (such as memory impairment, aphasia, and the inability to plan and initiate complex behaviour).</p>
